text: Le Vernet-Chaméane is a commune in the Puy-de-Dôme department in Auvergne in central France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Vernet-la-Varenne (the seat) and Chaméane.Arrêté préfectoral 23 November 2018 ==See also== *Communes of the Puy-de-Dôme department ==References== * INSEE commune file Vernetchameane
title: Le Vernet-Chaméane
